WEBVTT

00:02.832 --> 00:04.199
Do you want Adrian
to have the baby?

00:04.200 --> 00:05.667
What are we gonna do
with a baby?

00:05.668 --> 00:07.535
I'm okay with
whatever you wanna do.

00:07.536 --> 00:10.271
- I don't wanna have a baby.
- You don't have to.

00:10.272 --> 00:12.207
I don't want you and Ricky
to be anywhere near each other.

00:12.208 --> 00:14.242
I see the way he looks at you,
and I see the way you look at him.

00:14.243 --> 00:17.746
I am not interested
in you living at our house.
But you find a place to live.

00:17.747 --> 00:19.914
No one's gonna get in the way
of my life with Amy and John.

00:19.915 --> 00:22.851
- Unless Adrian has your baby.
- I am... mov-ing.

00:22.852 --> 00:25.019
- Where you moving?
- Maybe the guest house.

00:25.020 --> 00:28.757
If you're too scared
to stay out there by yourself,
maybe I could crash with you.

00:28.758 --> 00:30.759
Deep down, you have
a really big heart

00:30.760 --> 00:32.560
and a good conscience,
and you wanna do
the right thing.

00:32.561 --> 00:34.162
Is it right to bring a baby
into the world

00:34.163 --> 00:36.598
when I don't want that baby
and Ben doesn't want that baby?

00:36.599 --> 00:38.366
You're the one who suggested
I go out and have

00:38.367 --> 00:40.401
indiscriminate,
meaningless sex.

00:40.402 --> 00:43.438
You didn't have to
if you didn't want to.
You're jealous.

00:43.439 --> 00:45.573
I can't believe I have
my own apartment in New York.

00:45.574 --> 00:47.175
Don't forget,
it's a four-week life.

00:47.176 --> 00:48.610
We'll need you back here
after four weeks.

00:48.611 --> 00:50.111
You're my daughter,

00:50.112 --> 00:51.946
and I don't want you
to terminate the pregnancy.

00:51.947 --> 00:53.448
You can't decide that.

00:53.449 --> 00:55.583
Then maybe we really
shouldn't be a family.

00:55.584 --> 00:58.419
I want to take care of you.

00:58.420 --> 00:59.921
Will you marry me?

