that could help get her
into Juilliard.

06:14.291 --> 06:16.226
When my aunt was in high school,

06:16.227 --> 06:18.294
she got into a music program,

06:18.295 --> 06:22.365
and, uh, she stayed there
for...nine months.

06:25.569 --> 06:27.003
