06:28.672 --> 06:31.341
Wait.

06:31.342 --> 06:34.110
You don't think that Amy's
pregnant again, do you?

06:34.111 --> 06:36.012
No, Ashley, I don't.

06:36.013 --> 06:38.882
Well, I hope not.
There's no more room at the inn.

06:38.883 --> 06:41.351
I'll see you at home.
