28:02.496 --> 28:04.364
[ringing]

28:05.966 --> 28:06.900
Hello?

28:08.502 --> 28:10.670
Adrian?
Um, no. It's just me.

28:10.671 --> 28:12.205
I was trying
to call Adrian.

28:12.206 --> 28:14.707
She left her phone at home.
I have her phone.

28:14.708 --> 28:17.744
Oh, right.
Um, well, that makes sense.

28:19.413 --> 28:22.916
Okay, well, um, I'm sorry.
I hope you find her.

28:22.917 --> 28:24.784
Me, too, Ashley.

28:24.785 --> 28:26.553
Good night.

28:26.554 --> 28:28.088
[beeps]

28:30.691 --> 28:32.525
inging]

28:34.195 --> 28:35.662
[beeps]
Hello?

28:35.663 --> 28:37.397
Oh. Hi, Grace.

28:37.398 --> 28:39.365
It's me, Ruben,
Adrian's dad.

28:39.366 --> 28:41.668
Is everything okay?
No, not really.

28:41.669 --> 28:44.337
Adrian left us a note
saying she'd be back tomorrow,

28:44.338 --> 28:46.272
and we don't know where she is.

28:46.273 --> 28:48.708
And we're really
worried about her.
Is she there?

28:48.709 --> 28:51.377
No. But maybe
she'll come here.

28:51.378 --> 28:54.047
And if she does come here,
I'll have her call you
right away. I promise.

28:54.048 --> 28:55.381
All right.

28:55.382 --> 28:57.917
Thanks, Grace.

