She left her phone at home.
That's how I have your number.

29:07.394 --> 29:08.495
Okay. I'm sorry.

29:08.496 --> 29:10.396
That's okay. Good night.

29:10.397 --> 29:12.565
Good night.
[beeps]

29:15.870 --> 29:17.370
I need help.

29:17.371 --> 29:18.738
You haven't seen Adrian,
have you?

29:18.739 --> 29:20.073
No.

29:20.074 --> 29:22.041
I have a bad feeling
about this.

29:22.042 --> 29:24.511
I have bad stomach.

29:24.512 --> 29:27.447
Where's our new doctor dad?

29:27.448 --> 29:28.748
He and Mom
already went to bed.

29:28.749 --> 29:29.916
Of course.

29:29.917 --> 29:31.251
What's wrong
with your stomach?

29:31.252 --> 29:33.019
You're not a doctor.

29:33.020 --> 29:35.155
Don't try doctor me.

29:39.493 --> 29:42.128
[sniffs]
Ahh!

29:45.599 --> 29:48.635
[scoffs]
[door closes]

29:51.639 --> 29:53.740
I got cookies.

29:53.741 --> 29:55.408
Cookies?

29:55.409 --> 29:58.178
I got cookies.

29:58.179 --> 30:00.046
Who are you talking to?

30:02.650 --> 30:04.851
The gho-o-ost.

30:07.955 --> 30:09.889
Is that Jack's bag?

30:09.890 --> 30:11.624
That's Jack's gym bag,
isn't it?

30:11.625 --> 30:14.761
No-o-o-o-o.

30:14.762 --> 30:16.763
[phone ringing]
[Grace]
Is this where Jack is living?

30:16.764 --> 30:19.799
In the guest house with you?
He's not here.

30:19.800 --> 30:21.167
Are you sure about that?

30:21.168 --> 30:22.835
He gave me a ride.

30:22.836 --> 30:24.771
That his bag.

30:24.772 --> 30:27.373
He leave it here,
but he's not here.

30:28.809 --> 30:30.476
What's that?

30:30.477 --> 30:33.646
Brownies. Have one.
Trick or treat.

30:33.647 --> 30:36.015
What?
Go ahead.

30:36.016 --> 30:39.352
[sniffing]

30:39.353 --> 30:41.287
Where did you get these?

30:41.288 --> 30:43.223
The freezer.
Ohhh.

30:43.224 --> 30:45.725
I bet that homeless guy
left them here.

30:45.726 --> 30:48.027
Remember that homeless guy
that Dad used to let stay here?

30:48.028 --> 30:51.231
The one who was an alcoholic,
and he wouldn't go to AA
or anywhere else for help?

30:58.072 --> 31:00.006
It's actually
kind of nice in here.

31:00.007 --> 31:03.643
Why don't you sta-a-ay?

31:03.644 --> 31:05.945
Maybe I wi-i-ill.

31:05.946 --> 31:07.947
Maybe I'll just sleep here.

31:07.948 --> 31:09.949
I don't really feel
like being alone.

31:09.950 --> 31:11.918
And I can't quit thinking
about Adrian.

31:14.154 --> 31:16.089
Hey, can you
give me your phone?

31:17.491 --> 31:19.659
[beeping]

31:19.660 --> 31:21.094
[phone ringing]

31:22.162 --> 31:23.529
[beeps]
Tom?

31:23.530 --> 31:25.498
It's Grace.
Who's this?
Ruben.

31:25.499 --> 31:27.867
Oh. Right. Sorry.

31:27.868 --> 31:29.869
I thought Adrian might answer
if Tom called,

31:29.870 --> 31:31.537
so I called
using Tom's phone,

31:31.538 --> 31:34.741
but you have
Adrian's phone.

31:34.742 --> 31:38.911
I hate when other people
use other people's phones
to call.

31:38.912 --> 31:42.148
But anyway,
I've been praying about this--

31:42.149 --> 31:44.651
about Adrian--
and I have to believe

31:44.652 --> 31:46.653
that everything
will be fine.

31:46.654 --> 31:49.255
No matter where she is,
everything will be fine.

31:49.256 --> 31:53.259
It has to be, Mr. Ruben.

31:53.260 --> 31:54.394
Enriquez.

31:54.395 --> 31:56.296
And Enriquez to you.

31:56.297 --> 31:57.764
Good night.
[beeps]

31:59.867 --> 32:00.800
[beeps]

32:09.009 --> 32:11.944
Whose house is this?
Who is he cheating with?

32:11.945 --> 32:13.946
I don't know.
But it's curfew.

32:13.947 --> 32:15.948
We can't stay out here
all night.

32:15.949 --> 32:17.884
How could he
do this to me?

32:17.885 --> 32:19.252
Again, I don't know.

32:19.253 --> 32:21.921
I shouldn't have given him
the cow for free.

32:21.922 --> 32:25.291
I beg your pardon?
I thought he liked
getting the cow for free.

32:25.292 --> 32:27.560
Okay, snap out of it.
You're not a cow.

32:27.561 --> 32:29.595
You're a willing participant

32:29.596 --> 32:31.464
in whatever it is you're doing,

32:31.465 --> 32:33.499
and you are enjoying it
just as much as he is.

32:33.500 --> 32:35.735
He's obviously not
enjoying it as much as I am,

32:35.736 --> 32:38.604
or he wouldn't
be cheating on me.

32:38.605 --> 32:40.940
[sighs]

32:40.941 --> 32:42.709
[phone ringing]

32:47.981 --> 32:49.749
[beeps]
Hello?

32:49.750 --> 32:51.684
<i>Ruben?
Yeah?</i>

32:51.685 --> 32:53.586
Leo Boykewich.

32:53.587 --> 32:56.889
I just wanted to let you know
that Adrian's over here.

32:56.890 --> 32:59.559
I talked to her,
and I told her to call you,

32:59.560 --> 33:02.762
but I got a feeling
she's not going to.

33:02.763 --> 33:06.099
She left us a note that said
she'd be back in the morning.

33:06.100 --> 33:09.402
Cindy and I are fighting,
and she got upset.

33:09.403 --> 33:12.205
I don't want her
to have an abortion, Leo.

33:12.206 --> 33:14.974
I don't know
what you're thinking.

33:14.975 --> 33:17.577
I don't even care
what you're thinking,
or Cindy.

33:17.578 --> 33:20.346
I don't want her to do this.

33:20.347 --> 33:22.281
Can't you talk to Ben?

33:22.282 --> 33:24.650
Can't he talk her out of it?

33:24.651 --> 33:27.120
Wait. I forgot
who I'm talking to.

33:27.121 --> 33:30.089
Why would he talk her out of it?
He doesn't want that baby.

33:30.090 --> 33:31.891
It's not a matter
of what he wants,

33:31.892 --> 33:33.459
it's a matter
of what she wants.

33:33.460 --> 33:35.561
I know that's how
it should be.

33:35.562 --> 33:38.965
But, Leo, please.

33:38.966 --> 33:41.501
Do something.
Somebody do something.

33:41.502 --> 33:44.837
Look, I'll see to it she gets
back to you safely tomorrow,

33:44.838 --> 33:47.607
and that she goes from here
to there, all right?

33:47.608 --> 33:49.542
Unless you want her
to come home right now.

33:51.545 --> 33:54.781
Let her stay here.
e's with Ben.

33:54.782 --> 33:57.116
I think it's good for them
to have some time together.

33:57.117 --> 33:58.885
Haven't they spent
enough time together?

33:58.886 --> 34:01.421
Come on, Ruben.
She's fine here.

34:01.422 --> 34:04.457
All right.
I'm just happy she's safe.

34:04.458 --> 34:08.860
- Me, too. Good night.
- Thanks. Good night.

